The paper discusses the application of deep learning systems for autonomous driving, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also introduces a new approach for utilizing human intelligence in the form of crowdsourcing, which can be categorized under human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The evaluation of learning systems is also discussed, which can be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and robotics (cs.RO).
